POLIOMYELITIS UPDATE (35): VACCINE DERIVED POLIOVIRUS TYPE 2 ENVIRONMENTAL SAMPLES (USA, UK, ISRAEL), GLOBAL WILD POLIOVIRUS TYPE 1, CIRCULATING VACCINE DERIVED POLIOVIRUS TYPE 1, CIRCULATING VACCINE DERIVED POLIOVIRUS TYPE 2
